org.sakaiproject.portal.api

Interface PortalHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AtomHandler, BasePortalHandler, DirectToolHandler, ErrorDoneHandler, ErrorReportHandler, GalleryHandler, GalleryResetHandler, HelpHandler, LoginHandler, LogoutHandler, NavLoginHandler, OpmlHandler, PageHandler, PDAHandler, PresenceHandler, ReLoginHandler, RoleSwitchHandler, RoleSwitchOutHandler, RssHandler, SiteHandler, SiteResetHandler, StaticHandler, StaticScriptsHandler, StaticStylesHandler, TimeoutDialogHandler, ToolHandler, ToolResetHandler, TransformHandler, WorksiteHandler, WorksiteResetHandler, XLoginHandler

    public interface PortalHandler
    Tools that want to add handlers into the portal URL space may impliment this interface. The once injected into the portal the portal will invoke the register and deregister methods as part of the life cycle.
    Since:
    Sakai 2.4
    Version:
    $Rev: 105079 $
    Author:
    ieb
